.TH "prayertime-cli" "1" "Mar 2026" "prayertime-cli" ""

.SH NAME
prayertime-cli-times - Fetch daily prayer times and countdowns


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBprayertime-cli times [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Fetch daily prayer times and countdowns for a resolved location.

.PP
Contract:
  - Provide exactly one location input strategy: --query  or --lat with --lon.
  - --output text prints human-readable output to stdout.
  - --output json prints structured JSON to stdout.
  - --output value prints only the selected --field value.
  - Human-readable errors go to stderr. With --output json, errors are JSON on stdout.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for times


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--output\fP="text"
	Output mode: text, json, or value


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBprayertime-cli(1)\fP, \fBprayertime-cli-times-countdown(1)\fP, \fBprayertime-cli-times-get(1)\fP
